# Agent git workflow (gtcx-core)

Read: `docs/operations/agent-git-workflow.md`

## Defaults (do not ask)

1. **Commit** — micro-commit after each Class R story when gates pass. Never ask "should I commit?" or "commit or WIP?"
2. **Push** — at bout check-in when branch is ahead; `git push -u origin HEAD`. Never say "say push if you want."
3. **Overrides** — `do not commit` / `do not push` in user message wins for the session.

## Report (P27)

Status Update **Done**: `commit <sha>` · `git push` exit N — not delegation to operator.
